snippet.textDisplay:
Oh martyrs of the right path, oh ye (symbolic) pictures of loyalty!
The winds of thy nation send their Salam unto you. 
Oh martyrs of the right path...

Those that came to burn down this house of ours
You put the flames out by pouring your blood on them

You have saved countless flowers from orphanage 
Saved countless women from becoming widows

The skies of this garden (country) send their Salam unto you.
